Package app.controller.oauth.util.request

Class UrlBuilder

java.lang.Object
app.controller.oauth.util.request.UrlBuilder
public class UrlBuilder
extends java.lang.Object
Constructs url. Gets protocol and domain when initialising. Later variables can be added to a urlBuilder. Finally, you can get final url using build().
